&lt;p data-start=&quot;798&quot; data-end=&quot;1086&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate is equal parts relationship builder, operator, and growth driver. You are comfortable managing executive-level partnerships, creating scalable activation plans, and collaborating cross-functionally to translate strategic opportunities into measurable business results.&lt;/p&gt;
