&lt;li&gt;Proven track record owning pricing, promotions, and revenue growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong instincts for portfolio optimization (not just launches)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to zoom out to category strategy and zoom in to executional detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical, scrappy, and highly accountable — you know how to find and pull the right levers&lt;/li&gt;
